DOC.HEADLINE: BESCHEN MAKES FINALS AT HUNTINGTON BEACH
DOC.TEXT: Shane Beschen of San Clemente qualified for the finals of the Katin Team Challenge surfing competition Saturday on the north_side of the Huntington Beach Pier . Four top pros advanced to today ' s finals , including world champion Kelly Slater . Tag-team quarterfinals begin at 7 a.m. today , with individual and team finals beginning at noon .
